 <span data-ttu-id="00e7e-162">Das folgende Beispiel ist Teil einer benutzerdefinierten Sprachsynthese Implementierung, die von <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>verwendet wird, und verwendet die <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>Verwendung <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>von <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>,, und.<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e7e-162">The example below is part of a custom speech synthesis implementation inheriting from <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>, and using the use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEventId></span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="00e7e-163">Die Implementierung von<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="00e7e-163">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
